{"tid":1158276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侍應開錯$4.5萬佳釀奉客 英扒房食客叫$2612紅酒","createTime":"2019-05-17T00:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T01:06:51.000Z","uid":3090,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a90cdde7f7b8b8c3c331cece9a4e2f9e53ad0e","tid":1158276,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDNiSBC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDNiSBC.png&h=514a6432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「Hawksmoor」侍應誤拿貴十幾倍的佳釀奉客。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n英國一間高級餐廳擺烏龍，周二誤將一支值4,500鎊（45,222港元）的佳釀，當成值260鎊（2,612港元）的紅酒奉客。<br />\n<br />\n一位食客在曼徹斯特「Hawksmoor」扒房叫了一支值260鎊（2,612港元）的「Chateau Pichon Longueville Comtesse de Lalande 2001」，但因為侍應一時錯手，令他不知不覺間嚐到餐廳內唯一一支同年佳釀。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳周三在Twitter「分享」這宗意外：「希望那位早一晚意外品嚐到『Chateau le Pin Pomerol 2001』的食客那一餐吃得愉快；希望那位意外益食客的侍應振作。這是只此一次的意外，我們無論如何愛護你。」<br />\n<br />\n餐廳其中一位創立人貝克特（Will Beckett）表示，出錯的侍應羞愧得生自己的氣，但他相信侍應只是偶然犯錯，所以沒有怪他。貝克特說受惠的食客當晚一定喝得津津有味，因他還想多叫一支。<br />\n<br />\n網民爭相留言嘲笑餐廳一番，有人笑言光顧那餐廳時，會指定要那位送大禮的侍應招呼。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社／英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"de6ed781a9d291cf4b068f229b3619bc429dbc6e","tid":1158276,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:22:38.000Z","msg":"香港d waiter就學下人啦<br />\n<br />\n最多賠300咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb1f6685e8ed25bfcb3fc91ed2270c281d47433","tid":1158276,"uid":53798,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:23:57.000Z","msg":"愛回家情節"},{"pid":"3b6e300482b9ae41bd3135d8d4cd6b53bde1de30","tid":1158276,"uid":129379,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f1a90cdde7f7b8b8c3c331cece9a4e2f9e53ad0e","tid":1158276,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDNiSBC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDNiSBC.png&h=514a6432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「Hawksmoor」